{
  "texts": [
    "Each retrieved chunk was mapped to its source document, and the retrieved documents were evaluated by comparing them to a set of relevant documents for each query.",
    "Here we evaluate chunkers at a finer granularity than the previous experiment by measuring their abilities to locate evidence sentences.",
    "We selected additional datasets from RAGBench (Friel et al., 2024), shown in Tables 2 and 5, because few datasets contain long documents with ground-truth evidence sentences.",
    "We measured the number of ground-truth evidence sentences present in the retrieved top-k chunks.",
    "This experiment measured how chunkers impacted the quality of LLM-generated answers."
  ]
}